<dd>syllable</dd><br>
<dd>모음, 모음과 자음, 자음과 모음, 자음과 모음과 자음이 어울려 한 덩어리로 내는 말소리의 단위.</dd><br>
<dd>The unit of a speech that is pronounced as one lump, which includes a vowel, the combination of a vowel and a consonant, the combination of a consonant and a vowel, and the combination of a consonant, a vowel, and a consonant.</dd><br>
